DATA LICENSE NOTICE

The Sciweon code (this MIT license) is distinct from the data Sciweon
aggregates. Data sourced from upstream providers retains the original
licenses of those providers:

  - PubChem (NIH NCBI):       Public Domain
  - ChEMBL (EMBL-EBI):        Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0
  - ClinicalTrials.gov:       Public Domain
  - OpenAlex (OurResearch):   Creative Commons Zero (CC0)
  - PubMed (NIH NCBI):        Public Domain
  - UniProt (EMBL-EBI):       Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
  - UniChem (EMBL-EBI):       Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
  - openFDA (US FDA):         Public Domain
  - KEGG (Kyoto University):  Academic Free / Commercial Restricted
  - Retraction Watch:         CC BY-NC 4.0 (non-commercial)
  - RxNorm (NLM):             Public Domain
  - Semantic Scholar:         Open Data Commons Attribution
  - PubChem BioAssay:         Public Domain
  - EU CTIS (EMA):            Public access, non-commercial preferred

Consumers of Sciweon data must comply with the most restrictive applicable
upstream license. Aggregated entity records carry provenance.sources fields
naming the original provider; check those before commercial redistribution.

Sciweon makes no warranty regarding upstream data accuracy or completeness.
Data flows through validated extraction pipelines but original-source
errors / retractions / corrections may not be reflected in real time.
